text: Jack Welsby is a rugby league footballer who plays as a or for St. Helens in the Super League. ==Background== Welsby was born in Blackbrook, St Helens, Merseyside, England. ==Career== In 2018 he made his Super League début for St. Helens against Hull FC. ==References== ==External links== *St Helens profile *SL profile *Saints Heritage Society profile Category:Living people Category:Rugby league halfbacks Category:St Helens R.F.C. players Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Nationality missing Category:2001 births
